---

<BaseLayout
	title="About — Vital Photography"
	description="About Vital Photography — bio, gear, and photographic philosophy."
>
	<main class="about">
		<div class="portrait-placeholder" aria-hidden="true"></div>

		<h1>About</h1>
		<p>
			[TODO: replace with your bio — a paragraph or two about who you are, how you got into
			photography, and what draws you to landscape/nature and street/urban work.]
		</p>

		<h2>Gear &amp; Philosophy</h2>
		<p>
			[TODO: replace with notes on the cameras/lenses you shoot with and your approach to
			photography — what you're chasing when you pick up a camera.]
